t": "performance and should there be any significant change in forecasted assumptions or estimates, including sales,", "bbox": [143.8, 986.5, 1077.5, 1007.3]}, {"text": "profitability and discount rate, the Company may be required to recognize an impairment charge.", "bbox": [143.8, 1011.5, 955.1, 1032.3]}, {"text": "Intangible amortization expense amounted to approximately $71.2 for 2018, $61.0 for 2017 and $46.0 for", "bbox": [185.5, 1061.5, 1067.8, 1082.3]}, {"text": "2016, respectively. The Company estimates that intangible amortization expense will be approximately $70.0 in", "bbox": [143.8, 1086.5, 1079.8, 1107.3]}, {"text": "2019 and approximately $68.0 to $59.0 annually over the next five years.", "bbox": [143.8, 1111.5, 755.8, 1132.3]}, {"text": "During the fourth quarter of 2017, the Company determined that a Consumer Domestic tradename should be", "bbox": [185.5, 1161.5, 1092.2, 1182.4]}, {"text": "re-characterized from indefinite lived to finite lived assets. This conclusion was based upon lower forecasted", "bbox": [143.8, 1186.5, 1052.5, 1207.4]}, {"text": "sales and profitability and competitive pressures. This change was made after the annual impairment test was", "bbox": [143.8, 1211.5, 1055.6, 1232.4]}, {"text": "performed in which an impairment was not indicated. The carrying value of this tradename as of December 31,", "bbox": [143.8, 1236.5, 1072.1, 1257.4]}, {"text": "2017 was approximately $22.0 million and is being amortized over 20 years based upon the estimated cash flows.", "bbox": [143.8, 1261.5, 1094.0, 1282.4]}, {"text": "73", "bbox": [608.6, 1465.8, 629.4, 1486.6]}]}